sql_json.natural_language: Which of our team replied to accounts@vervewater.co.za most recently?
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE 'accounts@vervewater.co.za' IN UNNEST(toEmails) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
